      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "In commit \"scripted-diff: replace gArgs with a local args manager\" (af069fcdd9b5e2c983ee32f0292c8e1f167359ec)\r\n\r\nIn the commit message for https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/af069fcdd9b5e2c983ee32f0292c8e1f167359ec.patch you need an extra newline between the subject and body of the commit for the scripted diff to work like:\r\n\r\n```\r\nscripted-diff: replace gArgs with a local args manager\r\n\r\n-BEGIN VERIFY SCRIPT-\r\nsed -i -e '205!s/gArgs/argsman/g' src/test/getarg_tests.cpp\r\n-END VERIFY SCRIPT-\r\n```",
